1
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:13,560
Sister Qin.

2
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:18,480
But I can't play the harmonica anymore.

3
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,320
Xiaoxiong.

4
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,120
Don't worry.

5
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:30,920
I will find the best doctors in Harbin

6
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,400
to treat your hands.

7
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,680
In the future,

8
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:37,720
you will still be able to play the harmonica for everyone.

9
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,280
Where is my harmonica?

10
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:58,800
Xiaoxiong!

11
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,600
Xiaoxiong!

12
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,060
What's wrong with you?

13
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,040
Xiaoxiong!

14
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:04,960
Xiaoxiong!

15
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,280
Xiaoxiong!

16
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,680
Xiaoxiong!

17
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,240
Xiaoxiong!

18
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,540
Xiaoxiong!

19
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,360
Xiaoxiong!

20
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,210
Xiaoxiong! Xiaoxiong!

21
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,610
Xiaoxiong, wake up!

22
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,010
Xiaoxiong, wake up!

23
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,480
Xiaoxiong!

24
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,860
She treated Xiaoxiong like her own brother.

25
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,360
This hurdle

26
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,570
is too hard to overcome.

27
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,040
Chen Yu said

28
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:56,250
the Japanese never intended to let Xiaoxiong go.

29
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,579
They released him openly,

30
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,720
but secretly gave him an injection.

31
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,720
Sister Qin,

32
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:45,800
I joined the Harmonica Society to use music as a weapon,

33
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,360
to make the harmonica my second gun,

34
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,200
to promote resistance against Japan and save the country,

35
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:52,130
and to stop those young people from becoming slaves to a ruined nation.

36
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,280
Sister Qin,

37
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,200
I want to hold an open-air concert

38
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,920
at the entrance of our Harmonica Society.

39
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,320
Besides playing 'The Song of the Volga Boatmen',

40
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,800
'Carmen', 'La Traviata',

41
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,680
and 'Autumn Moon over the Calm Lake',

42
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,200
I also want to play our 'Battlefield Moon'

43
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:05,000
and 'Riding the Wind and Waves'.

44
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,240
To awaken the youth,

45
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,200
unite more cultural figures,

46
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,130
and fight against Japan together.

47
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,280
Our music is the bullet,

48
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,760
and the broadcasting station is the best gun barrel.

49
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,640
Otherwise,

50
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,000
we can't turn our Harmonica Society

51
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,930
into the second gun of resistance.

52
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,280
Miss Qin,

53
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,800
we've been waiting here for two hours

54
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,540
and twenty-nine minutes.

55
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,260
Captain Matsuda won't see you today.

56
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,210
Why don't you go back first?

57
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,260
I want to wait a little longer.

58
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:28,080
Captain Matsuda has been

59
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,840
investigating the underground party's radio station recently.

60
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,960
He's very busy.

61
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,520
Notify them.

62
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,880
The meeting is at four o'clock.

63
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,480
Yes.

64
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,400
Mr. Matsuda.

65
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,360
Miss Qin,

66
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,880
sorry to keep you waiting.

67
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,720
It's fine.

68
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,980
I know you're busy.

69
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,440
We're old friends.

70
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,560
I believe you wouldn't mind.

71
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,600
Of course not.

72
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,920
Mr. Matsuda,

73
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,530
you broke your promise.

74
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,050
I'm very disappointed.

75
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,010
What do you mean?

76
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,720
If I remember correctly,

77
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,160
you promised me last time

78
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,100
to let those children go back.

79
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,320
I'm here today to ask you,

80
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,800
when will you let those children go home?

81
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:22,560
Is Mr. Gu alright?

82
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,180
Mr. Gu should be recovering well,

83
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,800
right, Miss Qin?

84
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,520
Gu Xiaoxiong

85
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,850
doesn't deserve to die.

86
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:01,080
These were found in Gu Xiaoxiong's house:

87
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,640
anti-Japanese leaflets

88
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,240
and anti-Japanese slogans.

89
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:08,800
He is not only an anti-Manchurian and anti-Japanese element,

90
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,800
he is also

91
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,940
an underground party member.

92
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,200
In an hour, the Japanese army

93
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:26,360
will raid Taihe Inn, Qingfeng Grain Shop,

94
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:28,520
and our western medicine transit station.

95
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:30,920
Taihe Inn hides the list of contact points.

96
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:33,240
Qingfeng Grain Shop has winter cotton clothes.

97
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,679
And the western medicine transit station

98
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,320
has the penicillin for the assault team.

99
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:38,280
If these three places are taken out,

100
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,919
the sacrifice of our comrades will be too great.

101
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,000
Comrade Dajiang said

102
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,440
we must within half an hour

103
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,840
send out the intelligence.

104
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,800
Half an hour.

105
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,080
The intelligence is split into two parts:

106
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,240
contact point coordinates and the Japanese raid route.

107
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,720
The route map cannot be sent directly,

108
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,120
it needs to be converted into code first.

109
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,580
There's another problem.

110
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,960
The transmitter is destroyed.

111
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,040
Sending a message now

112
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:58,280
is very easy to be located by Suzuki Kang.

113
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,410
It's too dangerous.

114
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,680
Finish sending within three minutes,

115
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:03,600
and retreat immediately.

116
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,000
But what if...

117
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,060
There is no what if.

118
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,440
So many comrades are waiting for us to save them.

119
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,800
No matter how dangerous, we must send it out.

120
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:10,330
Brother,

121
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,360
drive faster.

122
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,080
Lingzi.

123
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,120
Convert the route map into code

124
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,320
and let Cheng Lin and Su Ying send it out.

125
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:24,960
Okay.

126
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,160
It's 8:15 now.

127
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,840
Start sending exactly at 8:40.

128
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,570
Understood.

129
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:32,340
See you at the advertising agency in 20 minutes.

130
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,040
Miss Qin,

131
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:36,810
there are patrolling military police ahead.

132
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,960
Mr. Zhang, turn left.

133
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,320
Sister Qin said that within three minutes,

134
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,840
the route map must be completely sent.

135
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,900
We must ensure the task is completed.

136
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:10,160
That radio station on Xinshi Street is transmitting again.

137
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,690
What is the exact location?

138
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,200
Shunfa Advertising Agency.

139
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:15,330
I will definitely catch him this time.

140
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,800
Team One, follow me.

141
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:36,840
Team Two, follow Deputy Section Chief Chen.

142
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,880
Surround the advertising agency.

143
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,720
Arrest the underground party. Move out!

144
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,560
Yes, sir.

145
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,520
Somebody!

146
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,160
Quick, open the door.

147
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,120
Open the door!

148
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,520
Open it!

149
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,560
Open the door!

150
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,120
Kick it down!

151
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,240
Uncle Gao might not be able to handle it alone.

152
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,680
Let's go down and help him.

153
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,280
Be careful.

154
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:39,880
Okay.

155
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,120
Brothers,

156
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,120
charge!
